name: Dealr
body:
### Business cards are tricky business.
Everyone uses them, but it's a pain getting them out. You can't hold them in your sweaty palms all day, and if you put them in your pockets you'll end up handing out someone else's card. You could use a business card holder and show everyone how complicated you can make simple tasks. Or, use Dealr, and retrieve each card in the blink of an eye.
